article.headline: Neal scores 15 as Idaho downs NAIA-member Evergreen State 88-42
article.description: — EJ Neal scored 15 points as Idaho beat NAIA-member Evergreen State 88-42 on Tuesday.
article.linkText: Neal scores 15 as Idaho downs NAIA-member Evergreen State 88-42
article.story: MOSCOW, Idaho -- — EJ Neal scored 15 points as Idaho beat NAIA-member Evergreen State 88-42 on Tuesday. Neal added six rebounds and three steals for the Vandals (1-2). Kyson Rose scored 13 points and added five rebounds. Terren Frank had nine points and was 3-of-8 shooting and 3 of 4 from the free-throw line. The Geoducks were led by Mubarak Michael, who posted eight points. Elijah McLaughlin added seven points for Evergreen State. Jayden Upshaw also had six points and two steals. ------+ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
